headline: 1 Cash-Producing Stock to Target This Week and 2 That Underwhelm
summary: Generating cash is essential for any business, but not all cash-rich companies are great investments. Some produce plenty of cash but fail to allocate it effectively, leading to missed opportunities.

headline: Labcorp expands PathAI pact to roll out digital pathology platform in US
summary: Labcorp’s pathologists will use the software to review, interpret and manage digital images of slides for primary diagnosis.
